The paper deals with the problem of rumor detection in news articles, which involves natural language processing and machine learning techniques. This suggests that it could belong to several sub-categories in computer science, such as Information Retrieval (cs.IR) for search and retrieval, Computational Linguistics (cs.CL) for language understanding, Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) for machine learning, Machine Learning (cs.LG) for model training and evaluation, and Social and Information Networks (cs.SI) for analyzing news propagation.
